726827f-a.folder: Greenpoint Avenue & Van Dam Street, Queens, NY
726827f-a.original_title: Queens: Greenpoint Avenue - Van Dam Street
726827f-a.text:
Intersection of Greenpoint Avenue (right) and Van Dam Street (left), looking east from Review Avenue. Back on Greenpoint Avenue can be seen St. Raphaels (R.C.) Chureh.
P. L. Sperr  July 27, 1940

726831f-a.folder: Greenpoint Avenue & Review Street, Queens, NY
726831f-a.text:
Greenpoint Avenue, east from Review Avenue. View 2 shows the avenue's intersection with Van Dam Street (left). In the background is St. Raphaels Roman Catholic Church, at Hunters Point
Avenue.
July 25, 1939
P.L. Sperr
